HEADWORD: Catawbas
<hw>Ca*taw"bas</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>;
<sing><it>sing.</it> <singw>Catawba</singw>.</sing> <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld>
